---
import SiteNav from '../../components/SiteNav.astro';
const currentPath = Astro.url.pathname;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<meta name="description" content="Design System — Design Document. Single source of truth for visual and interaction design." />
		<title>Design System — Design Document</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;0,9..40,700&family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
		<style is:global>
			@font-face {
				font-family: "Knockout 94";
				src: url("/fonts/knockout/Knockout-HTF94-UltmtSumo.otf") format("opentype");
				font-weight: normal;
				font-style: normal;
				font-display: swap;
			}

			@font-face {
				font-family: "Knockout 47";
				src: url("/fonts/knockout/Knockout-HTF47-Bantamweight.otf") format("opentype");
				font-weight: normal;
				font-style: normal;
				font-display: swap;
			}

			@font-face {
				font-family: "Gotham Book";
				src: url("/fonts/gotham/gothambook-webfont.woff") format("woff");
				font-weight: normal;
				font-style: normal;
				font-display: swap;
			}

			@font-face {
				font-family: "Gotham Bold";
				src: url("/fonts/gotham/gothambold-webfont.woff") format("woff");
				font-weight: 700;
				font-style: normal;
				font-display: swap;
			}

			:root {
				--color-bg: #faf9f7;
				--color-text: #1a1a1a;
				--color-muted: #5c5c5c;
				--color-accent: #2d5a4a;
				--color-border: #e5e3e0;
				--font-sans: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
				--font-serif: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
				--max-width: 720px;
				--toc-width: 220px;
			}

			* {
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			body {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
				font-family: var(--font-sans);
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: var(--color-text);
				background: var(--color-bg);
			}

			.page-wrap {
				max-width: calc(var(--toc-width) + var(--max-width) + 3rem);
				margin: 0 auto;
			}

			.doc-layout {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: var(--toc-width) 1fr;
				gap: 3rem;
				align-items: start;
			}

			.doc-toc {
				position: sticky;
				top: 2rem;
			}

			.doc-toc-title {
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.08em;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
			}

			.doc-toc nav {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 0.125rem;
			}

			.doc-toc-accordion {
				border: none;
				padding: 0;
				margin: 0;
			}

			.doc-toc-trigger {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: space-between;
				width: 100%;
				padding: 0.35em 0 0.35em 0.5rem;
				margin-left: -0.5rem;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				text-align: left;
				background: none;
				border: none;
				border-left: 2px solid transparent;
				cursor: pointer;
				font-family: inherit;
				gap: 0.5rem;
			}

			.doc-toc-trigger:hover {
				color: var(--color-accent);
			}

			.doc-toc-trigger::-webkit-details-marker {
				display: none;
			}

			.doc-toc-trigger .doc-toc-chevron {
				flex-shrink: 0;
				transition: transform 0.2s ease;
				opacity: 0.7;
			}

			.doc-toc-accordion[open] .doc-toc-chevron {
				transform: rotate(90deg);
			}

			.doc-toc-trigger a {
				flex: 1;
				color: inherit;
				text-decoration: none;
			}

			.doc-toc-trigger a:hover {
				color: var(--color-accent);
			}

			.doc-toc-trigger a.active {
				color: var(--color-accent);
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.doc-toc-accordion:has(.doc-toc-trigger a.active) .doc-toc-trigger {
				border-left-color: var(--color-accent);
			}

			.doc-toc-panel {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 0.125rem;
				padding: 0.25rem 0 0.5rem 0.75rem;
				margin-left: 0.25rem;
				border-left: 1px solid var(--color-border);
			}

			.doc-toc-panel a {
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				text-decoration: none;
				padding: 0.2em 0;
				display: block;
			}

			.doc-toc-panel a:hover {
				color: var(--color-accent);
			}

			.doc-toc-panel a.active {
				color: var(--color-accent);
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.doc-toc-item:not(.doc-toc-accordion) {
				padding: 0.35em 0 0.35em 0.5rem;
				margin-left: -0.5rem;
				border-left: 2px solid transparent;
			}

			.doc-toc-item:not(.doc-toc-accordion) a {
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				text-decoration: none;
				display: block;
			}

			.doc-toc-item:not(.doc-toc-accordion) a:hover {
				color: var(--color-accent);
			}

			.doc-toc-item:not(.doc-toc-accordion) a.active {
				color: var(--color-accent);
				border-left-color: var(--color-accent);
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.doc-layout {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
					gap: 1.5rem;
				}

				.doc-toc {
					position: static;
					padding-bottom: 1rem;
					border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
				}

				.doc-toc nav {
					flex-direction: column;
				}

				.doc-toc-trigger {
					padding: 0.4em 0.5em;
					margin-left: 0;
					border-left: none;
					border-radius: 3px;
					background: var(--color-border);
				}

				.doc-toc-panel {
					margin-left: 0;
					padding-left: 1rem;
					border-left-color: var(--color-border);
				}

				.doc-toc-item:not(.doc-toc-accordion) a {
					padding: 0.25em 0.5em;
					margin-left: 0;
					border-left: none;
					border-radius: 3px;
					background: var(--color-border);
				}
			}
		</style>
		<style is:global>
			.doc {
				max-width: var(--max-width);
			}

			.doc-header {
				margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
				padding-bottom: 2rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
			}

			.doc-title {
				font-family: var(--font-serif);
				font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
				font-weight: 400;
				margin: 0 0 1rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
			}

			.doc-lead {
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				margin: 0;
				font-style: italic;
			}

			.doc section {
				margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
			}

			.doc h2 {
				font-family: var(--font-serif);
				font-size: 1.35rem;
				font-weight: 400;
				margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
				color: var(--color-text);
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
			}

			.doc h2:first-of-type {
				margin-top: 0;
			}

			.doc h3 {
				font-size: 1rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
				color: var(--color-text);
			}

			.doc h4 {
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				margin: 1rem 0 0.35rem;
				color: var(--color-muted);
			}

			.doc-palette {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
				gap: 1.5rem;
				margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
				padding: 0;
			}

			.doc-palette-4 {
				grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
			}

			.doc-palette-3 {
				grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			}

			.doc-palette-item {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.75rem;
			}

			.doc-palette-item dl {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.doc-palette-item dt {
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				color: var(--color-text);
				margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
			}

			.doc-palette-item dd {
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				line-height: 1.4;
			}

			.doc-swatch {
				display: inline-block;
				width: 1.25rem;
				height: 1.25rem;
				border-radius: 3px;
				border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
				flex-shrink: 0;
			}

			.doc-swatch-lg {
				width: 7rem;
				height: 7rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
			}

			.doc-swatch-grey-100 {
				background: #f3f4f6;
			}

			.doc-swatch-gr-grey {
				background: #6b6b6b;
			}

			.doc-color-tabs {
				margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
			}

			.doc-tablist {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 0.25rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
			}

			.doc-tablist [role="tab"] {
				padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				font-family: inherit;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				background: none;
				border: none;
				border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
				margin-bottom: -1px;
				cursor: pointer;
			}

			.doc-tablist [role="tab"]:hover {
				color: var(--color-text);
			}

			.doc-tablist [role="tab"][aria-selected="true"] {
				color: var(--color-accent);
				font-weight: 500;
				border-bottom-color: var(--color-accent);
			}

			.doc-tabpanel {
				padding-top: 0.25rem;
			}

			.doc-tabpanel[hidden] {
				display: none;
			}

			.doc-font-families {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 1.25rem;
				margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
			}

			.doc-font-sample {
				padding-bottom: 1.25rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
			}

			.doc-font-sample:last-child {
				border-bottom: none;
				padding-bottom: 0;
			}

			.doc-font-label {
				display: block;
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.06em;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.doc-font-usage-label {
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.05em;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				margin: 0.75rem 0 0.35rem;
			}

			.doc-font-usage {
				list-style: none;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				line-height: 1.5;
			}

			.doc-font-usage li {
				margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
			}

			.doc-font-usage li::before {
				content: "– ";
				color: var(--color-accent);
			}

			.doc-font-knockout-94,
			.doc-font-knockout-47,
			.doc-font-gotham-book,
			.doc-font-gotham-bold {
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				line-height: 1.35;
				color: var(--color-text);
			}

			.doc-font-knockout-94 {
				font-family: "Knockout 94", sans-serif;
			}

			.doc-font-knockout-47 {
				font-family: "Knockout 47", sans-serif;
			}

			.doc-font-gotham-book {
				font-family: "Gotham Book", Gotham, sans-serif;
			}

			.doc-font-gotham-bold {
				font-family: "Gotham Bold", Gotham, sans-serif;
				font-weight: 700;
			}

			.doc-typography-note {
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				font-style: italic;
				margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
			}

			.doc-headers {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 1.5rem;
				margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
			}

			.doc-header-sample {
				padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
			}

			.doc-header-sample:last-child {
				border-bottom: none;
				padding-bottom: 0;
			}

			.doc-header-level {
				display: inline-block;
				font-size: 0.7rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				font-family: var(--font-sans);
				color: var(--color-muted);
				background: var(--color-border);
				padding: 0.2em 0.5em;
				border-radius: 3px;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.doc-header-body {
				font-family: var(--font-sans);
				font-size: 1rem;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
			}

			.doc-header-section,
			.doc-header-main,
			.doc-header-heavy,
			.doc-header-medium,
			.doc-header-light,
			.doc-header-alt-heavy {
				font-family: var(--font-serif);
				margin: 0;
				line-height: 1.3;
			}

			.doc-header-section {
				font-family: "Knockout 94", sans-serif;
				font-size: 2rem;
				font-weight: 400;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.12em;
			}

			.doc-header-main {
				font-family: "Knockout 94", sans-serif;
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				font-weight: 400;
				text-transform: capitalize;
			}

			.doc-header-heavy {
				font-family: "Knockout 47", sans-serif;
				font-size: 2.25rem; /* 4xl */
				font-weight: 700;
				text-transform: capitalize;
			}

			.doc-header-medium {
				font-family: "Gotham Bold", Gotham, sans-serif;
				font-size: 1.15rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.1em;
			}

			.doc-header-light {
				font-family: "Gotham Bold", Gotham, sans-serif;
				font-size: 1.15rem;
				font-weight: 700;
			}

			.doc-header-alt-heavy {
				font-family: "Gotham Book", Gotham, sans-serif;
				font-size: 1.875rem; /* 3xl */
				font-weight: 400;
				text-transform: uppercase;
			}

			.doc p {
				margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
				color: var(--color-text);
			}

			.doc ul {
				margin: 0 0 1rem;
				padding-left: 1.25rem;
			}

			.doc li {
				margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
				color: var(--color-muted);
			}

			.doc li strong {
				color: var(--color-text);
			}

			.doc hr {
				border: none;
				border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
				margin: 2rem 0;
			}

			.doc .note {
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				color: var(--color-muted);
				font-style: italic;
				margin-top: 2rem;
			}

			.doc code {
				font-size: 0.9em;
				background: var(--color-border);
				padding: 0.15em 0.4em;
				border-radius: 3px;
			}

			.doc a {
				color: var(--color-accent);
				text-decoration: none;
			}

			.doc a:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="page-wrap">
			<SiteNav currentPath={currentPath} />
			<div class="doc-layout">
			<aside class="doc-toc" aria-label="Table of contents">
				<p class="doc-toc-title">On this page</p>
				<nav>
					<details class="doc-toc-accordion doc-toc-item" open>
						<summary class="doc-toc-trigger">
							<a href="#overview-heading" onclick="event.stopPropagation()">1. Overview &amp; principles</a>
							<span class="doc-toc-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▸</span>
						</summary>
						<div class="doc-toc-panel">
							<a href="#purpose">1.1 Purpose</a>
							<a href="#principles">1.2 Design principles</a>
							<a href="#brand">1.3 Brand positioning</a>
						</div>
					</details>
					<details class="doc-toc-accordion doc-toc-item">
						<summary class="doc-toc-trigger">
							<a href="#foundations-heading" onclick="event.stopPropagation()">2. Foundations</a>
							<span class="doc-toc-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▸</span>
						</summary>
						<div class="doc-toc-panel">
							<a href="#color">2.1 Color</a>
							<a href="#typography">2.2 Typography</a>
							<a href="#typography-fonts">Font families</a>
							<a href="#typography-headers">Headings and subheads</a>
							<a href="#spacing">2.3 Spacing &amp; layout</a>
							<a href="#motion">2.4 Motion &amp; animation</a>
							<a href="#iconography">2.5 Iconography</a>
							<a href="#imagery">2.6 Imagery &amp; media</a>
						</div>
					</details>
					<details class="doc-toc-accordion doc-toc-item">
						<summary class="doc-toc-trigger">
							<a href="#components-heading" onclick="event.stopPropagation()">3. Components</a>
							<span class="doc-toc-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▸</span>
						</summary>
						<div class="doc-toc-panel">
							<a href="#component-template">3.1 Component template</a>
						</div>
					</details>
					<details class="doc-toc-accordion doc-toc-item">
						<summary class="doc-toc-trigger">
							<a href="#patterns-heading" onclick="event.stopPropagation()">4. Patterns</a>
							<span class="doc-toc-chevron" aria-hidden="true">▸</span>
						</summary>
						<div class="doc-toc-panel">
							<a href="#layout-patterns">4.1 Layout patterns</a>
							<a href="#navigation">4.2 Navigation</a>
							<a href="#forms">4.3 Forms &amp; inputs</a>
							<a href="#feedback">4.4 Feedback &amp; status</a>
							<a href="#content-patterns">4.5 Content patterns</a>
						</div>
					</details>
					<div class="doc-toc-item">
						<a href="#a11y-heading">5. Accessibility</a>
					</div>
					<div class="doc-toc-item">
						<a href="#responsive-heading">6. Responsive &amp; platform</a>
					</div>
					<div class="doc-toc-item">
						<a href="#governance-heading">7. Governance &amp; maintenance</a>
					</div>
					<div class="doc-toc-item">
						<a href="#appendix-heading">8. Appendix</a>
					</div>
				</nav>
			</aside>
			<article class="doc">
			<header class="doc-header">
				<h1 class="doc-title">Design System — Design Document</h1>
				<p class="doc-lead">Single source of truth for visual and interaction design. Use this to keep Figma, brand, and product work consistent. Code implementation references this document.</p>
			</header>

			<section aria-labelledby="overview-heading">
				<h2 id="overview-heading">1. Overview &amp; principles</h2>

				<h3 id="purpose">1.1 Purpose</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>This system is for AOPA's digital design & branding.</li>
					<li>It serves devs, design and content producers.</li>
				</ul>

				<h3 id="principles">1.2 Design principles</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>
						Clear Communication
					</li>
					<li>Simplified Structures</li>
					<li>Impactful Patterns</li>
					<li>REfined Typography</li>
				</ul>

				<h3 id="brand">1.3 Brand positioning</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Mission, voice, and personality in 1–2 paragraphs.</li>
					<li>How the design system supports the brand (tone of UI, imagery, motion).</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<hr />

			<section aria-labelledby="foundations-heading">
				<h2 id="foundations-heading">2. Foundations</h2>

				<h3 id="color">2.1 Color</h3>
				<div class="doc-color-tabs">
					<div class="doc-tablist" role="tablist" aria-label="Color palettes">
						<button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="color-panel-primary" id="color-tab-primary">Primary</button>
						<button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="color-panel-ycf" id="color-tab-ycf">You Can Fly</button>
						<button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="color-panel-foundation" id="color-tab-foundation">Foundation</button>
						<button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="color-panel-asi" id="color-tab-asi">Air Safety Institute</button>
					</div>
					<div id="color-panel-primary" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="color-tab-primary" class="doc-tabpanel">
						<h4>Primary palette</h4>
						<div class="doc-palette">
							<div class="doc-palette-item">
								<span class="doc-swatch doc-swatch-lg" style="background: rgb(22, 51, 114);" aria-hidden="true"></span>
								<dl>
